creator: KAMA.SPORT SRL
descriptionHtml:
Kama. is the app for football professionals. Data analysis, video, scouting and much more, all at your fingertips.

Are you interested in Italian football? Access to Serie A, B and C data and highlights.

Analyze each match in detail.
Explore players and teams.
Compare them and find weaknesses and strengths.
Access up-to-date and accurate information.
Watch videos and highlights through an optimized selection and search system.
Discover new talent.
Organize training sessions and matches.
Study statistics and reports to improve your job and skills in football.

Kama. it is a comfortable, useful and innovative tool, to always carry with you.

Kama. is technology for sports clubs and professionals, football between passion and data, the detail that makes the difference.
Kama. it is selection, integration and personalization.

The Kama. Staff is available: send us reports and feedback to app@kama.sport.
Support the project by voting the Kama. app with 5 stars, it is important to us.
